Here's the corrected PlantUML sequence diagram for `hyeonsangjeon_youtube-dl-nas`:

```plantuml
@startuml hyeonsangjeon_youtube-dl-nas

actor User
participant WebBrowser
participant "Web Server\n(Bottle)" as WebServer
participant "Auth Service" as AuthService
participant "Queue Manager" as QueueManager
participant "Download Worker" as DownloadWorker
participant "yt-dlp" as YTDLP
participant "WebSocket" as WebSocket
database "Auth.json" as AuthDB

User -> WebBrowser: Accesses Web Interface
WebBrowser -> WebServer: GET /login
WebServer -> WebBrowser: Serve login.tpl

User -> WebBrowser: Enters credentials
WebBrowser -> WebServer: POST /login (credentials)
WebServer -> AuthService: Validate credentials
AuthService -> AuthDB: Query credentials
AuthDB --> AuthService: Return auth data
AuthService --> WebServer: Authentication result

alt Authentication Success
    WebServer -> WebBrowser: Redirect to /index
    WebBrowser -> WebServer: GET /index
    WebServer -> WebBrowser: Serve index.tpl
    WebBrowser -> WebSocket: Establish WS connection
    
    User -> WebBrowser: Submits download URL
    WebBrowser -> WebServer: POST /download (URL)
    WebServer -> QueueManager: Add to queue
    QueueManager -> DownloadWorker: Notify new job
    
    loop While jobs in queue
        DownloadWorker -> QueueManager: Get next job
        DownloadWorker -> YTDLP: Execute download
        YTDLP --> DownloadWorker: Download progress
        DownloadWorker -> WebSocket: Send progress
        WebSocket -> WebBrowser: Update UI
    end
    
    DownloadWorker -> WebSocket: Send completion
    WebSocket -> WebBrowser: Show completion
else Authentication Failed
    WebServer -> WebBrowser: Return error
end

@enduml
```